{
    "description": "Push-up Phase 2 extension: continue k=2 for 10K more steps on fresh data. Load k=2 20K checkpoint. data_seek = 7680512 (k=2 start) + 20000*512 (k=2 consumed) = 17920512. Tests whether L0+L1 find equilibrium with more joint training.",
    "model": {
        "d_model": 512,
